@startuml NetPulse_时序图_设备管理
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title NetPulse — 时序图：保存设备（新增或编辑）

actor "运维用户" as U
participant "浏览器" as FE
participant "DeviceController\n/api/devices" as DC
participant "DeviceService" as DS
participant "DeviceRepository" as DR
participant "AuditService" as AD
database "MySQL" as DB

U -> FE: 填写设备表单、提交
FE -> DC: POST 或 PUT /api/devices\n{ Device JSON }

DC -> DS: save(device)

DS -> DR: save(entity)
DR -> DB: INSERT 或 UPDATE
DB --> DR: 持久化结果
DR --> DS: Device

DS --> DC: Device

DC -> AD: log(CREATE_DEVICE 或 UPDATE_DEVICE, ...)
AD -> DB: INSERT audit_log

DC --> FE: 200 Device

note right of FE
  仅 ADMIN 可在表单中查看/提交
  SSH、SNMP 密码等敏感字段；
  见 DeviceList 权限逻辑。
end note

@enduml
